import React from 'react';
import { Navbar, Nav, Container, Button, Form, FormControl, NavDropdown, Image } from 'react-bootstrap';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';



function Header() {
  return (
    <Navbar bg="white" expand="md" fixed="top" className="shadow-sm">
      <Container>
        {/* Logo */}
        <Navbar.Brand as={Link} to="/" className="text-primary" style={{ fontFamily: 'Pacifico', fontSize: '2rem' }}>
          FishingHub
        </Navbar.Brand>

        <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="main-navbar-nav" />

        <Navbar.Collapse id="main-navbar-nav">
          {/* Navigation */}
          <Nav className="me-auto">
            <Nav.Link as={Link} to="/" className="text-primary fw-medium border-bottom border-primary pb-1">
              Trang chủ
            </Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link as={Link} to="/shop" className="text-secondary fw-medium">
              Sản phẩm
            </Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link as={Link} to="/event" className="text-secondary fw-medium">
              Sự kiện
            </Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link as={Link} to="/newfeed" className="text-secondary fw-medium">
              Bài viết
            </Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link as={Link} to="/knowledge" className="text-secondary fw-medium">
              Kiến thức
            </Nav.Link>
          </Nav>

          {/* Auth Buttons */}
          <Button
            as={Link}
            to="/login"
            variant="outline-primary"
            className="rounded-pill me-2"
          >
            Đăng nhập
          </Button>
          <Button
            as={Link}
            to="/register"
            variant="primary"
            className="rounded-pill"
          >
            Đăng ký
          </Button>
        </Navbar.Collapse>
      </Container>
    </Navbar>
  );
}

export default Header;
